originalText.text: I went here back on Sept 1st of this year for my Gender Ultrasound, and it was absolutely amazing the girl at the front desk was so nice and made me & my family feel so comfortable. They even gave me a little care package for baby which was so thoughtful. I got one of the cutest videos of my baby kissing the placenta that I can't stop watching, I am now going back to see my babies' features. I will always recommend Beli's 5D to anyone that is looking for an elective ultrasound. I love this place :)

originalText.text: Wow so many positive things to say. Evelyn made me feel welcome from the minute we spoke on the phone. She was amazing and so was the receptionist. They answered all of my questions and gave me so many recommendations and tips. They also took their time to explain the process step by step. We got to see our baby clearly, and got the best images and video. The belly cast was done very net, professional, and fast. Can’t wait to see the finish product. Overall a positive vibe, I will be back soon to do other services when baby is born or when I have another pregnancy.  The best experience ever, I absolutely loved it. Thank you so much.
